.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, jet-ski, train, van
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, gospel, folk, salsa, country
House: townhouse, art-deco, cottage, palace, farmhouse
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, nurse, writer, social-worker, bartender
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the motorbike
2. the fan of gospel is the owner of the dog
3. the security-guard is the person driving the skateboard
4. the fan of folk is the nurse
5. the person driving the skateboard is to the right of the person driving the jet-ski
6. the townhouse house is the owner of the snails
7. the art-deco house is the person driving the train
8. the writer is in the middle
9. the fan of salsa is on the far left
10. the cottage house is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the art-deco house is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the palace house is the social-worker
13. the fan of country is the farmhouse house
14. the fan of salsa is to the left or right of the person driving the van

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Music-Genre	|   salsa	|    folk	|     hip-hop	|    gospel	|    country	|
| Transport		|    train	|      van	|      motorbike	|     jet-ski	|     skateboard	|
| Job	|     bartender	|      nurse	|      writer	| social-worker	|     security-guard	|
| House		|     art-deco	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| palace	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
